# Validators layer rules

## Module ownership

- `schema_validator.py` — JSON-LD structured-data schema validation only. **No workbook I/O** — this package must not import from `reporter/` or write cells.

## Invariants

- Validators enrich/inspect row dicts **read-only**; never mutate the row dict passed in.
- Must not raise on malformed input — flag or annotate the row instead (e.g. via a `skip_reason`-style field) so a single bad JSON-LD block never aborts a crawl.
